QUICK START SUMMARY
================================================================================

1. Install Python 3.8+
2. Install Node.js + npm
3. Clone/download project
4. Backend:
   cd backend
   python -m venv venv
   venv\Scripts\activate
   pip install -r requirements.txt
   python app.py

5. Frontend (new terminal):
   cd frontend
   npm install
   npm start

6. Open: http://localhost:3000

